---
layout: v2/layout.njk
title: Curated Lists
permalink: "/v2/lists/"
---

<section>
  <p>Curated collections of FAQs organized for specific audiences and use cases. Each list contains carefully selected questions most relevant to that topic or role.</p>
</section>

<nav>
  {% for list in data.lists %}
    <a href="/v2{{ list.permalink }}/">
      <h2>{% if list.icon %}{{ list.icon }} {% endif %}{{ list.title }}</h2>
      <p>{{ list.description }}</p>
      <p><strong>{{ list.faqs.length }} FAQs</strong></p>
    </a>
  {% endfor %}
</nav>
